metadata.name: BoredApeLuxury.club Mint Pass
metadata.description: Expanding on the BAYC franchise, us here at Yuga Labs have now officially partnered with the designer brand GUCCI. You'll be able to unlock brand new skins, accessories, wearables and much more. It pays to be an Ape and there's nothing more luxury than being in the Bored Ape Luxury Club. Show off your luxury side and use your items in-game within the Otherside.
